252
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:14,100
-The idea of a bank being the guardian--
-Stop this nonsense, Jim.

253
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:16,900
"We will assume full management
of the Colorado Lode"...

254
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:19,500
