415
00:27:59,400 --> 00:28:01,800
You know, Mr. Bernstein...

416
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:06,000
...if I hadn't been very rich...

417
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:08,800
...l might have been a really great man.

418
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:10,900
Don't you think you are?

419
00:28:12,900 --> 00:28:15,900
I think I did pretty well
